    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Documents maintained by or relating to a particular mosque and its activities, including for many public functions; religious, political, social, and educational. Schools and libraries and courts of justice were attached to mosques until the introduction of secular law into many Islamic countries in modern times, so records of these functions may be included.</Note_Text>
